						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of land as <hi rend="italic">mañjikkam</hi> by the <hi rend="italic">sabhā</hi> of Veḷichchēri in Puliyūrkōṭṭam for the maintenance of a perpetual lamp and for offerings during the two services in the temple of <hi rend="bold">Kāḷā-Bhaṭāri.</hi> This is left incomplete.</p>						

						</summary>
